Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那家伙又出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透说要去朋友家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连别人说话都不会听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那家伙难得一见的出门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就说明小透已经完全融入这个家了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家的娇花现在在何处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照波鸟的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞒着草摩他们 过这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hallo！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}红 红叶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 来到草摩家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波家在这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像没人住一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人更紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这路有那么累人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红叶 弄点喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja（好）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点意外 他会放女性的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉十分严肃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得说话的时候就像在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的话是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该 该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要教训什么都不会的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小波看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没没事 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 总之坐吧坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 波鸟医院…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作那边没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我是只看这一族的人的草摩家庭医生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大半都是在照顾慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的特技就是瞬间生病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天草摩家的人都很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有人来看病的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在准备正月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是最重要的活动嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不单单是内部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外部成员也要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部？外部？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家的人就叫做内部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透来这里的时候有一条林荫道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在那一带的人就被称为外部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 有一百多人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部大概有五十人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是草摩家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这还真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能住在内部的人包括我们十二生肖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及知道这个秘密的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前小紫和由希都住在内部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹在外部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来说就是知道十二生肖秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一族中也只是很少一部分人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘密竟然被你这个外人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:04:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是件大事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该是马上就要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出隐藏处置的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慊人却没有做出这个指示
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至同意你们住一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在紫吴家过得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 啊 是的 很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再和草摩扯上关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被妖怪附身的草摩家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是你想象中那么快乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇异
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你后悔和草摩家扯上关系之前 离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慊人只是想要利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左眼基本是看不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波以前有个女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做佳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经快要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是慊人生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且反对结婚 然后发飙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就伤了小波的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 小波并没有怪慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳菜十分自责
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得是自己让小波的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直自责
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终得了心病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波消除了佳菜的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他不忍看到遍体鳞伤的佳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以消除了他们相爱的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳菜离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是无法责怪慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这就是诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波再也不想让佳菜那样的人再出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让小透你和佳菜一样受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 哭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 弄哭你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为波鸟实在太温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 能遇到大家真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是因为被利用才有了现在的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反而觉得应该道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会后悔扯上关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了草摩他们 我才能有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遇到我高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会利用小透的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫吴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波说事情总爱夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直觉 直觉啊 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个小说家 第六感要很敏锐才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是来看正月的准备怎么样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡人总是爱嫉妒天才
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人也差不多别再活得像只水母了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那两个人 别看总是这样 他们可是发小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波 操心太多小心秃头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了几次了 慊人没有恶意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该相信相信我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还吓到小透
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如果真走了怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的谢谢你担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是要留在那个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着还没忘记就先给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是文化祭那时候的相机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么为什么 这是说好的交易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你过来的话 我就把那个相机给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来会怎么样 你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟和紫吴一样 是那种贯彻自己思想的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}什么 那个相机是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}烦死了 垃圾小说家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你还没见过慊人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 波鸟也是十二生肖之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么生肖？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又能笑一阵子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你四岁时候的羞耻的事告诉出版界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 总是惹你哭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小透 我去看一眼正月的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 要去练舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练舞？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是正月惯例那种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟 不能对小透动手动脚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么回见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 波鸟你和紫吴是发小吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听红叶说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是孽缘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你没事吧 波鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 海水 水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要哪种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本田透的反应和她一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是草摩佳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始我会作为助手而努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总觉得明明是一族人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没说过话 有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家的波鸟很帅 在外部也很有人气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得会下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以问个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪化了会变成什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是变成水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是会变成『春』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她对于我来说就像春天一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说被关在幽暗的笼子中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐冻成的『雪』是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是清新鲜明的『春』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱上她就如同必然一样水到渠成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 海水 水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪个啊 波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的把海马扔到澡堂子里肯定会死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我总算知道理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在想为什么你不肯抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被别人知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是会拉开和别人的距离吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对喜欢的人 就是更是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要拒绝我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 很高兴能遇到波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能喜欢上波鸟我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉从出生以来有什么被接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉被拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像冰冻的飞雪被春天的气息融化了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪止不住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后的两个多月就像做梦一样开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像十几年的幸福都凝缩在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦醒来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在请求慊人同意我们结婚的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会给你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}慊人 等一下 冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}慊人 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明无法解开诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果波鸟看不见了 就是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}佳菜 快带波鸟走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她病了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管说什么 做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都会崩溃得大哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她病了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她得了心病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候你的隐藏术就派上用场了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要消除她的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是别人 你不是做得很干脆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在让她痛苦的 正是和你的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对你的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她从这些痛苦中救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你最后该做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她其实也想被解放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许愿说 想要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有相遇就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是报应？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论受伤还是哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是命令所以没办法只能剥夺别人的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是报应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的人的记忆 自己最重要的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会亲手去消除他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法保护 你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能保护你的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 佳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不会再让你痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 很高兴能遇到波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次请让她遇到能真正让她幸福的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我永远被不会融化的雪包围也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是因为下面 那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裸着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 所以那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的十二生肖的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 但 但是我不觉得奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别出乎意料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鞋子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是在刚才那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 总算要结婚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜 佳菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你先生是什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起很安心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过脸还是波鸟比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这人又在这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很喜欢他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是以暗恋结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好想打招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你别花心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因为我现在可是热恋中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时隔两年见到她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时候一样笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 变得幸福了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在恭喜什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了 波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪今天那么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 请你 请你变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我永远被不会融化的雪包围也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪融化了会变成什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪融化了会变成什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 诶这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 会变成春天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就算再怎么寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天总会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不可思议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你送我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫吴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波 你骚扰小透了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波鸟那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自叫你出来 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他不是什么坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 晚饭吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫吴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒 究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不做真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要保持你的样子就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不是说的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草摩家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎明白了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又似乎什么都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是不可思议的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会正式和那个人见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉有本事让鬼都睡着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好了 你们快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不吃晚饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 那种重视的感觉是不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个家里生活的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要珍惜着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍惜着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这是差一点就忘记的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}差点忘记你总在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不论何时都触手可及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}给了我生活的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再见 珍重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}直到重逢的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感激 不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}总是面带着笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh please 比任何人都要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只要有你在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就能无比坚强 My heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不说离别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与明日紧紧相连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}奇迹一定会again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}来吧给这个纪念日 画上小红花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被大大的爱怀抱着 这个幸运的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}马上移开的是 这暧昧不明的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你已是多次 对我诉说着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}需要着朝阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:22:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想要慢下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}什么将要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心情愈发激荡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}总有一天我一定 会回应你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在这里让我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想要守护的那种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这不是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}紧紧相连的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如果被称作『羁绊』的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}everything changes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}everybody changes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请不要改变 一直留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一直留在这里
